{"tid":718118,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"中美貿易戰之變節","createTime":"2018-06-26T14:08:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T00:01:18.000Z","uid":109386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"30cfdf4864d0946ff4418fc592ddd62815b6bae4","tid":718118,"uid":109386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T14:08:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/amp/business-44611772\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Famp%2Fbusiness-44611772&d=jbrgomOfy58J3%2FUUrHu67KMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=82bffe12\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Famp%2Fbusiness-44611772&h=216c47e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/amp/business-44611772</a><br />\n<br />\n美國摩托車製造商哈雷戴維森（Harley Davidson，簡稱「哈雷」）宣佈要把生產線搬到歐洲後，引來美國政府反彈。美國總統特朗普在社交網站說，他對哈雷的決定感到驚訝，但分析卻認為哈雷這一步無法避免。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在社交網站發文，形容哈雷是「舉起白旗投降」，又指哈雷只是把歐盟的關稅威脅，變成自己把廠房搬到海外的借口。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟早前宣佈會向摩托車、波本威士忌和橙汁徵收額外關稅，報復美國對歐盟鋼材徵收巨額關稅。哈雷指，歐盟的措施令旗下摩托車的售價每輛平均增加2200美元，它必須擴大美國國外的生產線，避過歐盟對美國進口的關稅，才能繼續以具吸引力的價錢把摩托車賣到歐盟市場。<br />\n<br />\n晶片商岀唔岀到呢招技？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72109d6108aebdec7277f19c14ab01118534bf0e","tid":718118,"uid":109386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T14:09:47.000Z","msg":"A Harley-Davidson should never be built in another country-never! Their employees and customers are already very angry at them. If they move, watch, it will be the beginning of the end - they surrendered, they quit! The Aura will be gone and they will be taxed like never before!"},{"pid":"a22de17d0893fe2c0455f15dc2d8cf2e604df00b","tid":718118,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T14:16:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cb0bd992f430183f3c7be3a7e56b5c49ef6a4681","tid":718118,"uid":162272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"30cfdf